race.description: New England Shade Sails Country Boosted Hcp
race.comment: ZOOMORPHIC (3) had excuses at his last two outings and assess on the tough on-pace win at Scone three starts back. Comes out of a strong rating contest on the quick backup. LUCKY OZZIE (8) lightly raced gelding who looks a much stronger commodity this time in. At his peak for this from the inside draw after he gripped on late to finish fourth over 1400m at Inverell. Gets the right run and expected to go close. VISUALISE (6) up quickly in trip at his second run back when a plugging sixth over 1400m at Inverell. No surprise to see him push forward today and take a hand in the finish. AGE OF AQUARIUS (7) back in grade when a most improved second over this trip at Armidale. Trained on the track and represents good value despite drawing awkwardly.
